attributes.long-description:
Go! Puzzle™ includes three great puzzle sensations: Swizzle Blocks, Aquatica and Skyscraper. It's the ultimate test of speed, nerves and wits all rolled into FUN! Take it with you for instant puzzle action fun any time, anywhere!

KEY FEATURES
• Various Gameplay modes – Contains single, co-op and multiplayer challenges with various play modes and infinite levels.
• Swizzle Blocks features, 4 exhilarating modes including Puzzle, Challenge, Time Attack, and Battle.
• Aquatica features 3 fast paced modes, 50 brain cracking puzzles, and online video chat.
• Skyscraper features 3 mind-tickling modes, 7 cities, 5-7 towers each, and 50 brain-teasing puzzles.
• Game Sharing – Share the fun with a friend by uploading a demo of the game to your friends.
